00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,280
Then go back.

710
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:17,840
Let's go back together.

711
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:18,920
Come on.

712
00:35:21,630 --> 00:35:24,670
